{"tid":815811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（12/9）沙田區手足，你屋企有無唔見阿婆？","createTime":"2018-09-12T10:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T16:38:49.000Z","uid":202464,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"42e6e11e39b8f7c461d5ef9075b9d529a7c630ad","tid":815811,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:16:30.000Z","msg":"五點幾六點左右<br />\n<br />\n年約七十幾歲<br />\n<br />\n身高一米5<br />\n<br />\n瘦身裁<br />\n<br />\n拎住斜咩手袋<br />\n<br />\n拎住紅色皮製tote bag，內有書、紙扇、手持聖安娜麵包，遮一把<br />\n<br />\n佢一時唔記得自己住邊，亦無帶手提電話，係沙田大會堂附近盪失路，問本人借電話打。淨記得一個電話號碼26xx 34xx。但無人聽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人已經將阿婆交予沙田火車站既警察。<br />\n<br />\n如你地屋企有唔見阿婆，請聯絡沙田警署。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cd69ceb2e292fee894e2dacbb4940c77279544","tid":815811,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777a2deeb4939edd4bae7d5a52e2e346f828adfd","tid":815811,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"好心有好報"},{"pid":"9c789f4eaa9c504d0936b983d4fcf1ec24884bf0","tid":815811,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d428c23703f3395114bc694382c4c6a876e4c108","tid":815811,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b18d00056ae7c0bfb8a51d2d5b7e961276ceb8","tid":815811,"uid":33850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"4dd36dc6e5fe70257dcc1f22874c17a8d380f9e4","tid":815811,"uid":53089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:42:44.000Z","msg":"巴打好人有好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望婆婆冇事"},{"pid":"d2cb0711607486ba1bdb63ce706049438e0e6d20","tid":815811,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"個阿婆以前做慰安婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77256766fd84b0bc89baa7fcd044bf252862fc54","tid":815811,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:45:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打好人有好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望婆婆冇事</blockquote><br />\n正常就應該無事既。<br />\n<br />\n差佬會搵社署，阿婆本地人實有拎生果金果類，一定知住邊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過你地如果發現屋企有唔見阿婆就盡快接返佢啦。阿婆急得滯喊左架。"},{"pid":"01430aa09d6a4d4b0095edf3c788dddc94f04cda","tid":815811,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:46:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個阿婆以前做慰安婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本仔黎果陣佢未出世啦"},{"pid":"27907b8a2611b6fe458a835f089911680db40b2b","tid":815811,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"連登仔連阿婆都執到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e422953ce83300a78ea24ffbb2a92920957f62a2","tid":815811,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔連阿婆都執到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好似第三次執到野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾年前執到狗狗，幫佢搵返主人<br />\n<br />\n舊年執到貓b，不過最後救唔返。<br />\n<br />\n今日就阿婆。"},{"pid":"9751b2b61d46b3249436e3e5da3719e241f5ff80","tid":815811,"uid":74685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"執呀婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> pish"},{"pid":"f18fff42cb2f12230055c45b764b2aca76d1ed74","tid":815811,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9751b2b61d46b3249436e3e5da3719e241f5ff80","tid":815811,"uid":74685,"like":